 the\nSSD limit. Our field theory calculation is confirmed by a numerical study on a\n(1+1)-d critical fermion chain.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 21 Feb 2018 19:39:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 3 Apr 2018 18:44:05 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 21 May 2018 17:56:52 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 12 Jun 2018 04:29:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-13"}
