nd transport, and demonstrated with a few\napplications done with both classical and quantum-mechanical simulation\nmethods.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 22 Feb 2018 12:19:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 16 Aug 2018 18:51:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-20"}
